## 📝 Quickstart

### Basic

```shell
docker run -i --rm ghcr.io/toshy/docker-chadsay:latest Unit tests? We don\'t do that here.
```

![Chadsay git](./.images/chadsay.png)

### Multi-line

Using `$'\n'` for multiple lines.

```shell
docker run -i --rm ghcr.io/toshy/docker-chadsay:latest Changes 5000 lines of code$'\n'\> git commit -m \'minor changes\'$'\n'\> git push origin main$'\n'Leaves
```

![Chadsay git](./.images/chadsay_multiline.png)

### Dynamic content

With [NAAS (no-as-a-service)](https://github.com/hotheadhacker/no-as-a-service):

```shell
docker run -i --rm ghcr.io/toshy/docker-chadsay:latest $(curl -sL https://naas.isalman.dev/no | sed -n 's/.*\"reason":\"\([^"]*\)".*/\1/p')
```

![Chadsay NAAS](./.images/chadsay_naas.png)

[chadsay_naas]: <data:image/png;base64,>


### To your `.bashrc`

```shell
cat << 'EOF' >> ~/.bashrc
echo "$(docker run -i --quiet --rm ghcr.io/toshy/docker-chadsay:latest $(curl -sL https://naas.isalman.dev/no | sed -n 's/.*\"reason\":\"\([^"]*\)\".*/\1/p'))"
EOF
```

## ❗ Important

- This repository automatically builds docker images for [chadsay](https://github.com/agvxov/chadsay) based on the latest commit hash of the master branch.
- Bugs, questions or other issues not related to the docker image that is built here should be asked in [agvxov/chadsay](https://github.com/agvxov/chadsay) instead.
